---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="About | Petrol Nexus" path="/about">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>About Petrol Nexus</h1>
    <p>We are a global energy operations partner focused on safe production, modern infrastructure, and long-term resilience.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      <article class="card"><h3>Mission</h3><p>Power industries with reliable and responsible energy delivery.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Vision</h3><p>Lead the transition to smarter, lower-intensity energy operations.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Values</h3><p>Safety, transparency, engineering excellence, and innovation.</p></article>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
